Source: R/wnba_stats_team_dash.R
wnba_teamdashboardbyshootingsplits.Rd

Get WNBA Stats API Team Dashboard by Shooting Splits

Get WNBA Stats API Team Dashboard by Shooting Splits

Usage

wnba_teamdashboardbyshootingsplits(
  date_from = "",
  date_to = "",
  game_segment = "",
  last_n_games = 0,
  league_id = "10",
  location = "",
  measure_type = "Base",
  month = 0,
  opponent_team_id = 0,
  outcome = "",
  pace_adjust = "N",
  plus_minus = "N",
  po_round = "",
  per_mode = "Totals",
  period = 0,
  rank = "N",
  season = most_recent_wnba_season(),
  season_segment = "",
  season_type = "Regular Season",
  shot_clock_range = "",
  team_id = "1611661328",
  vs_conference = "",
  vs_division = "",
  ...
)
